text: Headed to Adi for compass QA meeting, back after lunch

<!channel> We had an a little discussion after our retro this week and I'm going to announce on the adi compass channel that we're canceling retros going forward due to code freeze and a shift in the way we'll be working going forward. 

We feel like retros need to be a "safe space" and it'd be great to continue having them, just without adidas folks (they don't usually show up anyway). Going forward, we'll have a retro from 4-4:30 on Friday afternoons where we can have a beer and talk candidly about the project. I really appreciated how honest everyone was today, it felt productive!
